summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the acquisition by negotiation or by condemnation of land and other property rights at the location commonly known as 1310 West Dravus Street, The West 35 feet of Lot 13, Block 35, Gilman's Addition to the City of Seattle, according to the plat thereof recorded in Volume 5 of Plats, page 93, records of King County, Washington, situate in the County of King, State of Washington, for general municipal purposes including, but not limited to, the expansion of Fire Station \#20.
committee: Public Safety, Governmental Relations and Arts
vote: 4-5 (In favor: Godden, Licata, McIver, Rasmussen) (Against: Clark, Conlin, Della, Drago, Steinbrueck)
